, Werbung und PR ist.  aOn the medial creation and distribution of stereotypes: The book addresses central theories and examinations about this and creates foundations for a new, trans-disciplinary field of research.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aMass mediaxSocial aspects. 0aPrejudices in mass media. 0aStereotypes (Social psychology) in mass media. 4aDiskriminierung. 4aKommunikationswissenschaft. 4aMedientheorie. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aMedienästhetik. 4aStereotype. 4aVorurteile. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aCommunication Research.  aDiscrimination.  aMedia Aesthetics.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia Theory.  aPrejudices.  aStereotypes.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2015z9783110438741oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839427248zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839427248423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839427248/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSWb2015  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016